'''''Leucidia''''' is a genus of [[butterfly|butterflies]] in the famlly [[Pieridae]]. They are native to the [[South America]].

==Species==
* ''[[Leucidia brephos]]'' <small>(H<U+00FC>bner, [1809])</small>
* ''[[Leucidia elvina]]'' <small>(Godart, 1819)</small>

